Viral Logic Systems Technology
	Developer of novel therapeutics for the treatment of inflammatory and autoimmune disorders. The company\'s product is used for the treatment of rheumatoid arthritis, Crohn\'s disease, multiple sclerosis, lupus nephritis, mixed cryoglobulinemia, Wegener\'s granulomatosis and diabetes.
