Actimis Pharmaceuticals
	Developer of small molecule therapeutics for respiratory, inflammatory and autoimmune diseases. The company offers its therapeutics for autoimmune diseases, such as asthma, chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD), inflammatory dermatoses, inflammatory bowel disease and rheumatoid arthritis.
