Immunex
	Provider of biopharmaceutical drug discovery. The company is focused on immune-system research, in the disciplines of immunology, cytokine biology, vascular biology, antibody-based therapeutics and small-molecule research. It works to develop new therapeutics for rheumatoid arthritis, asthma and other inflammatory diseases, as well as cancer and cardiovascular diseases.
	['', 'antibody therapeutics', ' ', 'vascular science', ' ', 'rheumatoid arthritis', ' asthma ', 'cardiovascular therapy', '']
Cornerstone Therapeutics
	Developer and distributor of products for respiratory, inflammatory and critical care diseases. The company focuses on the discovery, development and commercialization of products designed to treat asthma and critical care diseases through the regulation of the body’s inflammatory response.
